ambition</as>.</def> <au>Addison.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*bound"ed*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*bound"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
